11
00:00:34,990 --> 00:00:38,450
Days inventory, on the other hand,

12
00:00:38,450 --> 00:00:41,300
tells us how many days of inventory

13
00:00:41,300 --> 00:00:43,170
is on our balance sheet--

14
00:00:43,170 --> 00:00:46,850
so how much money we're tying up in inventory.

15
00:00:46,850 --> 00:00:49,650
And we want this number to be as small as possible.

